title: NFL ATL: First rookie QB to start
itunes:title: NFL ATL: First rookie QB to start
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- sift through the aftermath of the 2014 NFL Draft, breaking down which teams landed gems in New York City. Which teams can bank on throwing their rookie quarterback right into the mix? Which NFL veterans should be fearful of getting passed by? All these questions, and more, answered on this edition of the "Around the League Podcast."
